  "elapsed_s": 18.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What angers me, that her name is very well known in the Jewish community in Toronto, but instead of her, they erected a statue or a monument to Wallenberg, a CIA agent whose task was, if he could have pushed it through, there would have been a third world war starting right in Hungary, because they wanted to stop the Red Army, [INAUDIBLE], not to let the Bolsheviks into Western-- Western Europe.",
      "word_count": 72
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was his assignment from Dulles, who was sitting in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The billionaire-- you read the stories they wrote.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I saw it again, that they erected the statue for him in London-- but [INAUDIBLE] Bales Park [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bales Park there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted to go there to print a leaflet, but what the hell?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I haven't got so-- so much spare money to hand out the leaflet and expose this-- expose this guy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- I was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My contact was Karl Schandl Jr., who was an officer in the Hungarian army, and from the-- from the officer staff, the high command of the Hungarian army, [INAUDIBLE] dispersed information about it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Before I heard it from him, I heard rumors already, because of the Swedish-- Swedish embassy was so close, that this man is circulating around.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's-- he's pretending that he's-- he's saving Jews and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he's doing dirty things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He's going to the rich Jews and collecting money and-- and jewelry and so on and so forth, and he share it with the-- with the-- with the SS and so on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there was a confusion about the man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But somebody already-- already suspected from somewhere, because there were other people, probably, in the high command that they knew about-- about Wallenberg.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these things went around.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
